  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Good facilities are available, such as a swimming pool, fitness room, sauna and tennis court. This is one the medium budget hotels in the prime area of Silom, offering easy access to shopping, nightlife and mouth-watering cuisine.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is located south of Silom Road next to Bangkok Bank headquarters.  It is approximately 5-10 minutes walk from the main Silom Road. There is easy access to the Chongnonsri sky train station.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>The deluxe rooms are medium in size and modernly decorated. All are equipped with standard facilities. The bathrooms are small, yet clean.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is housed in a 5-storey white concrete low-rise building.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel has one main restaurant offering all-day dining and breakfast.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The medium-sized lobby has a small reception counter.</Text>
  </Description>
